  3. country.RData - contains genre country only

(Codes from the given Text_Processing.Rmd)

Step.8 Topic Modeling

code from Tutorial(Week 2) and tidytextmining

The goal is to make a heat map to see if Hiphop and Country lyrics share similar topics.

The dataset used in this step is new.RData. Use method and set k = 5 to get 5 topics from the hiphop and coutry lyrics. First convert the corpus to document term matrix. Then use LDA to get the topics and the terms in each topic by beta value. Then clustering the data frame and make the heat map.

Conclusion

By observing the word frequency, word cloud, sentimentGI score, emotions distribution and the topics analysis, we can conclude that Hip-hop and Country music lyrics are significantly different.

Hip-hop lyrics tend to be more negative. The words associated with âfearâ are used frequently. Whereas Country lyrics are more warm and positive. The words associated with âjoyâ are used frequently.

Eventhough two genresâ lyrics give different feeling, âLoveâ is the most popular theme for both.

This conclusion also consistent with our guess by the definitions and cultures.
